The '''hyperspace cannon''' was an early device used to achieve [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] travels.

==Characteristics==
Prior to the invention of the [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]], the hyperspace cannons were used by the first [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]] colonists to launch their [[Starship/Legends|starships]] into hyperspace. Once they had achieved lightspeed in this way, a vessel could then induce a drag element to slow back down and return to [[Realspace/Legends|realspace]].

==History==
Over the course of many centuries, a network of hyperspace cannons were developed, linking the newly-colonized Core Worlds with the [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] civilization.

